import streamlit as st



st.header('INTRODUCTION')
st.write('The "Flower Classification using Deep Learning" initiative focuses on creating an automated system capable of accurately identifying various flower species through the application of deep learning techniques. This project harnesses the capabilities of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) to learn and detect unique features in images of flowers, facilitating precise classification. By leveraging the advanced pattern recognition abilities of CNNs, the system aims to deliver highly accurate identification results.This automated classification system is designed to support botanists, gardeners, and flower enthusiasts in their efforts to identify flowers. By automating the classification process, the project aims to streamline and enhance the accuracy of flower identification, making it more accessible and efficient for users. The systems ability to accurately recognize different flower species can significantly aid in botanical research, gardening, and the enjoyment of flower enthusiasts.')
